{"tid":2496555,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"梁籌庭批評簽效忠聲明制度衍生篤背脊文化  他得悉有至少過萬宗相關個案。","createTime":"2021-04-20T02:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T03:35:12.000Z","uid":179775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"806ca4274b650396e6fcda510754717f9a295f88","tid":2496555,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:10:16.000Z","msg":"本地 發佈時間 20.04.2021 09:47最後更新時間 20.04.2021 09:47 政府指有129名公務員拒絕簽署擁護《基本法》聲明。公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭形容這批公務員「很勇」，犧牲事業去測試政府的底線，相信他們是年資較短的公務員。梁籌庭在本台節目上表示，自從政府要求公務員簽署聲明後，「篤背脊」文化變得盛行，曾經有新入職公務員被同事截取社交平台言論，指控他有政治表述，要交由公務員事務局處理，他得悉有至少過萬宗相關個案。 梁籌庭認為，現時公務員團隊的氣氛很差，人心惶惶，但政府無心解決，質疑局方有心助長「篤背脊」文化。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2388008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2388008&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuD%2BzTm40CM4Hl%2BPVqeZuRg0%3D&h=5594ee08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2388008</a><br />\n<br />\n萬幾個黃絲比藍絲篤灰"},{"pid":"a2be678384dc8645b91dd28947e287001206e670","tid":2496555,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77323a42b26a825f369a08adf63e68371b74a798","tid":2496555,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:20:11.000Z","msg":"後國安法時代係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"632e881de636fcbde199c6b4d7fc8cb5f093a09f","tid":2496555,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:21:18.000Z","msg":"篤走晒班後生<br />\n藍屍老屎忽做到八十歲先退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e7875eb977b0b2153bfb5cf120d7d2906ec28c","tid":2496555,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:22:03.00